{"tid":1674451,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[I/A] 整咗個live map用黎捉小精靈","createTime":"2019-10-25T08:19:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T05:06:54.000Z","uid":281850,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d4276b7dd904d6911d832ca59b636b5b41d8e5bd","tid":1674451,"uid":281850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T08:19:55.000Z","msg":"是咁的 最近覺得留喺條街捉小精靈都幾危險 所以諗諗下又整整下就整咗個app出黎 等大家都可以等到有小精靈出現嘅時候先至落街捉 以防大家捉到小精靈就翻唔到屋企陪隻小精靈玩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁呢隻app有咩做到嘅？<br />\n你可以公開你嘅捉小精靈情報又可以只同你嘅朋友分享 單機嘅話亦得 得咗<br />\n你又可以改下朋友send出黎嘅情報令到啲情報更加準確<br />\n你又可以評分話俾其他朋友知呢個情報有冇用 同時呢個app會根據你地俾嘅分去睇呢個情報有冇用 冇用嘅時候咁自然就要自動消失費事其他人見到以為仲喺度啦<br />\n緣分到仲會有個統計 統計下啲情報邊度出得最多 外加可以自定個list黎分類下啲比卡超出現過喺咩地方咁<br />\n<br />\nAndroid<br />\n<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.nativetech.rushcha\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.nativetech.rushcha&d=r5q0VKZH5TKX5M4XK8oFTXO0ZW31AiaZ%2BXmqixBX3cM%3D&h=762f702d\" target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.nativetech.rushcha</a><br />\n<br />\niOS<br />\n<a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/rushcha/id1482180604\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.apple.com%2Fus%2Fapp%2Frushcha%2Fid1482180604&d=r5q0VKZH5TKX5M4XK8oFTXO0ZW31AiaZ%2BXmqixBX3cM%3D&h=57303299\" target=\"_blank\">https://apps.apple.com/us/app/rushcha/id1482180604</a><br />\n<br />\n講明先只係俾捉小精靈用 如果唔係隻app會俾cook學院委員會主席落架架<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nsor for 1999+死p牌仔+第一次開po"},{"pid":"54cb779c2acc4dfaaee9c55d574d1c3e3a2c6e15","tid":1674451,"uid":281850,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T08:21:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ofd5zob.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fofd5zob.jpg&h=a3f7c64f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XWTM3gx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXWTM3gx.jpg&h=d3c73ab2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n附上兩張圖教點用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6b59fa97617d5c87d289de57f5d61d020c1d411","tid":1674451,"uid":7494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T08:28:53.000Z","msg":"有用post, 推<br />\n<br />\nbtw, 唔好意思, 借個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n鍾庭耀發起全港大型民調及公投嘅眾籌post, 需要大家支持<br />\n<br />\n(代POST)【本土X國際戰線】鍾庭耀發起全港大型民調及公投<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1659927\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1659927</a><br />\n<br />\n眾籌傳送門﹕<a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209&d=r5q0VKZH5TKX5M4XK8oFTXO0ZW31AiaZ%2BXmqixBX3cM%3D&h=a55814ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209</a>"},{"pid":"7d59dba1de07c188b2249eba77c4bfec68c4391a","tid":1674451,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T08:31:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"592e27ef23b6aed0b4b1ec7d6bb7e90773fbc8e8","tid":1674451,"uid":281850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T08:38:52.000Z","msg":"推10次先"},{"pid":"03274716ed271a125685e5d56a0cd7747f9c0de5","tid":1674451,"uid":281850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T08:39:44.000Z","msg":"0/10"},{"pid":"d09fe863cd894a5a5961682244726579afd007fd","tid":1674451,"uid":281850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T08:40:33.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"aff7e8d3146067d0d3203fcc4a2621b453f26dd5","tid":1674451,"uid":281850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T08:40:54.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"d3e7b6ca40c55f